Homepage: https://github.com/openyellowos

Package: oyo-sys-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash, whiptail, pciutils, usbutils, whiptail, pciutils, usbutils
Description: Utility scripts for open.Yellow.os (help-hw, oyo-check, pacup)
 This package provides helpful maintenance and diagnostic tools used in
 the open.Yellow.os distribution:
  - help-hw   : collect basic hardware logs (dmesg/lspci/lsusb)
  - oyo-check : system health checks (profile, disk, services, apt, etc.)
  - pacup     : package update helper
